      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried the doctors and the meds. nothing works. i'm just tired of fighting for a life that just feels like constant agony. i don't want to manage the pain anymore... i just want the peace of it all finally being over. it feels like the only mercy left would be just... not being here.",
